                     Hāymānot (e.g., <locus target="#6vb">6vb</locus>, 10vb, 14rb), his wife Walatta
                     Madḫǝn (e.g., <locus target="#13rb">13rb</locus>, 14rb, 22ra, 30ra), Zärʿa
